CASE ANNOUNCEMENT

December 16, 2010

[Cite as 12/16/2010 Case Announcements, 2010-Ohio-6140.]

MOTION AND PROCEDURAL RULINGS

2010-1551. State ex rel. Dreamer v. Mason.

Cuyahoga App. No. 93949, 2010-Ohio-4110. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Court of Appeals for Cuyahoga County. Upon consideration of the motion to seal appellants’ merit brief,

It is ordered by the court that the motion is granted.
